ars/48/upload/user99878.jpg"></div></div><div class="tcontent">多谢johndxy117战友。“粘膜下层内有大量平滑肌”不知有何依据？还是根据教材“固有层的外面还有粘膜肌层”，曾以为此“肌层”为划分二者的界限或标志，但有些组织粘膜肌层似乎缺如（还是不明显？），此时...</div><div class="attachment-box"></div></div><div class="topic-footer"><ul class="topic-user" data-user="fenghe2000"><li class="date">2010-05-24</li></ul><ul class="topic-operate"><li><a href="javascript:;" data-id="17273799" class="J-do-vote icon icon-vote "><span class="num"></span></a></li><li><a href="javascript:;" data-id="17273799" class="J-do-reward icon icon-reward "><span class="num"></span></a></li><li><a href="/bbs/reply/post/17273799?quote=true" class="icon icon-quote J-quote" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'detail', 'click', 'quote']);"></a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr id="topic_17705342"><td class="topic-detail"><div class="postbody"><div class="profile"><div class="txt"><div class="tinfo"><p class="name"><a href="/bbs/user/chinajpd#!page=1&amp;type=topic">chinajpd</a></p><div class="user-level-area">铁杆站友<p class="user-level user-level-3"></p></div></div></div><div class="avatar"><img src="//img.dxycdn.com/avatars/48/upload/911/940564-7BNf.jpg"></div></div><div class="tcontent">黏膜固有层是由介于疏松结缔组织和致密结缔组织之间的过渡结缔组织构成，黏膜下层是由疏松结缔组织构成，所以这两层结构还是可以大致区分的，比如下图气管结构中，固有层的细胞成分相对黏膜下层较多，固有层纤维排列...</div><div class="attachment-box"></div></div><div class="topic-footer"><ul class="topic-user" data-user="chinajpd"><li class="date">2010-07-15</li></ul><ul class="topic-operate"><li><a href="javascript:;" data-id="17705342" class="J-do-vote icon icon-vote "><span class="num">4</span></a></li><li><a href="javascript:;" data-id="17705342" class="J-do-reward icon icon-reward "><span class="num"></span></a></li><li><a href="/bbs/reply/post/17705342?quote=true" class="icon icon-quote J-quote" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'detail', 'click', 'quote']);">&nbsp;</a></li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="lPost-tipBox"><a href="https://auth.dxy.cn/login?service=http%3A%2F%2F3g.dxy.cn%2Fbbs%2F